WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.200
Oh Lord, how many are my foes.

2
00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:07.260
Many are rising against me.

3
00:00:07.260 --> 00:00:12.640
Many are saying of my soul, there is no salvation for Him in God.

4
00:00:12.640 --> 00:00:18.640
But You, O Lord, are a shield about me, my glory, and the lifter of my head.

5
00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:23.800
I cried aloud to the Lord, and He answered me from His holy hill.

6
00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:26.160
I laid down and slept.

7
00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:29.400
I woke again, for the Lord sustained me.

8
00:00:29.400 --> 00:00:37.040
I will not be afraid of many thousands of people who have set themselves against me all around.

9
00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:44.360
Arise, O Lord, save me, O my God, for You strike all my enemies on the cheek.

10
00:00:44.360 --> 00:00:46.760
You break the teeth of the wicked.

11
00:00:46.760 --> 00:00:49.840
Salvation belongs to the Lord.

12
00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:51.840
Your blessing be on Your people.

13
00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:53.840
The word of the Lord.

14
00:00:59.400 --> 00:01:07.160
When I was a kid, my parents had one of these baby first books.

15
00:01:07.160 --> 00:01:09.160
