17
00:01:14.160 --> 00:01:19.520
And I think my first words were like a lot of children's mama.

18
00:01:19.520 --> 00:01:23.520
And my second word was crystal.

19
00:01:23.520 --> 00:01:25.680
And it wasn't because we had a family member named Crystal.

20
00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:29.360
It's because I had learned that I liked fast food pretty early on.

21
00:01:29.360 --> 00:01:31.160
And so we'd go through the drive-through.

22
00:01:31.160 --> 00:01:33.840
